# Multi-Vendor E-Commerce Management Platform

## Project Description
This project is a full-stack multi-vendor e-commerce platform where multiple vendors can create stores and sell products while customers can browse and place orders.

## Features
- User authentication (Register / Login)
- Vendor store creation
- Product management
- Shopping cart
- Order management
- Role-based access (Admin, Vendor, Customer)

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB

### Frontend
- React
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios

## Project Structure

project-root
│
├── backend
